description: Arising from the pages of the Seeker series comes this special issue. Tracy LeMaster examines her past when she held the mantle of Seeker and now her new current role that has her labeled as "Gestalt". She believes she is serving an ancient ruler of Atlantis that has inhabited the host bodies of prior Seekers but is this all in her mind or is she truly tapped into the magic of that long forgotten archaic realm?
